nance. We hypothesize that SR-LO will significantly outperform static integration methods in handling complex linguistic phenomena such as metaphorical signs, negation scope, and long-range dependencies. The impact extends to low-resource multilingual translation and assistive AI systems where meaning preservation is paramount.",
